subject: World Cup (Skiing)
lead_paragraph: Lindsey Vonn failed to clinch the overall World Cup title after she clipped a gate, and Sandrine Aubert of France won her first World Cup race in the slalom in Germany.
snippet: Lindsey Vonn failed to clinch the overall World Cup title after she clipped a gate, and Sandrine Aubert of France won her first World Cup race in the slalom in Germany.
